rows.label: tev061801_MSG0001
rows.name:
Pulala hear that some human friends want to keep
Nopon as pets.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061801_MSG0002
rows.name:
So when Lucia invite Pulala into home,
warning bells definitely start to go off.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061801_MSG0003
rows.name:
But Pulala realize once living together that Lucia treat
Ma-non and Nopon equally.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061801_MSG0004
rows.name:
Now Pulala is sure that Lucia is good person.
Doubts all seem so silly![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061801_MSG0005
rows.name:
Pulala is looking forward to making many new friends
thanks to Lucia and nice home.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061801_MSG0010
rows.name:
Lately, no place in Mira is safe for Nopon.
Nopon get attacked everywhere![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061801_MSG0011
rows.name:
But Pulala saw human friends fighting here and there,
so came to city to get help.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061801_MSG0012
rows.name:
But the paperwork! Meh! Pulala have to jump through
so many hoops to get quest filed with Mission Control.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061801_MSG0013
rows.name:
Anyway, friend look much less tasty than Nopon,
but friend should still be careful if wandering outside.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061801_MSG0018
rows.name: Prone like to eat Nopon, so Pulala was terrified.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061801_MSG0019
rows.name:
But since living in same city with Prea Slarth,
Pulala realize that Tree Clan Prone are not so bad.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061801_MSG0020
rows.name:
When Pulala tell Prea Slarth that Prone out there are
still attacking and eating friends, Prea get worried.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061801_MSG0021
rows.name:
Just as worried as if member of own family was getting
eaten! Then Prea promise to look into it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061801_MSG0022
rows.name:
Pulala so grateful! It seem Pulala was one smart cookie
to come to city and make so many wonderful friends.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061801_MSG0027
rows.name:
Comm device of Pulala used to have "bee-bee-
bee-beep" ringtone for when message come in.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061801_MSG0028
rows.name:
But Gu Ludho so surprised upon hearing it that
Gu Ludho jump right onto roof![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061801_MSG0029
rows.name:
Then Gu Ludho explain that Ganglion weapons make
same noise when target is locked. ...Needless to say,
Pulala change ringtone immediately.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061801_MSG0030
rows.name:
Then Pulala agree to let Gu Ludho snuggle Pulala until
scary feelings went away.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061801_MSG0031
rows.name:
But Gu Ludho is also pretty fluffy, so it was like double
snuggle. Lots of static! Bzzzzt![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061801_MSG0036
rows.name:
Pulala and friends threw party to celebrate victory
over Ganglion![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061801_MSG0037
rows.name:
Grex-tongue pizza that Chanty make take bit of
getting used to...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061801_MSG0038
rows.name:
But everyone have great time talking all night about
food and fashion and places each is from.
Before Pulala know it, sun was coming up![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061801_MSG0039
rows.name:
Hee hee! Pulala cannot thank Lucia enough for letting
Pulala live in place with so many wonderful friends![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061801_MSG1001
rows.name:
Everyone can rest easy and get on with life now that
Blood-king is gone.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061801_MSG1002
rows.name:
Many thanks to friend! Nopon that get fried to crisp
can now rest in peace inside tree.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061801_MSG1003
rows.name:
Nopon go to very big tree after dying.
Did friend know this?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061801_MSG1004
rows.name: Friend say thanks to stuck-up fancy-pants friend, too![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061801_MSG1009
rows.name: Prone like to eat Nopon, so Pulala was terrified.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061801_MSG1010
rows.name:
But living in same city with Prea Slarth, Pulala realize
that Tree Clan Prone are not so scary.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061801_MSG1011
rows.name:
Once, Pulala tell Prea Slarth that Prone were attacking
and eating friends. Prea Slarth get just as worried as if
member of own family was getting eaten![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061801_MSG1012
rows.name:
It was Prea Slarth that figured out Blood-king was
behind string of mass devourings.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev061801_MSG1013
rows.name:
Pulala was so grateful! Pulala was smart to come to
city and make so many wonderful friends.[ST:wait ]
